PN,34901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FA special train named the Spirit of
OL,7,FInvictus has been unveiled to
OL,8,Fcelebrate the courage and resilience
OL,9,Fof wounded, injured and sick service
OL,10,Fpersonnel.
OL,12,FThe train is part of a one-year
OL,13,Fcountdown until the Duke of Sussex's
OL,14,Fmulti-sports event takes place in
OL,15,FBirmingham.
OL,17,FPresenter and former Invictus Games
OL,18,Fcompetitor JJ Chalmers, who revealed
OL,19,Fthe train at London's Euston Station,
OL,20,Fsaid he hopes it will help "empower"
OL,21,Fthose taking part.
OL,26,@|D@\OU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
