OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FChalmers, who was injured in a bomb
OL,7,Fblast in Afghanistan in 2011 while
OL,8,Fserving with the Royal Marines, said
OL,9,Fcompeting in the inaugural Invictus
OL,10,FGames in London in 2014 had given him
OL,11,Fa valuable chance to "serve again".
OL,13,FHe said that when Harry, who did not
OL,14,Fattend the launch, approached him to
OL,15,Fbe part of the games it was obvious it
OL,16,Fwould help people with their physical,
OL,17,Fmental and social recoveries.
OL,26,@sD@VOUsD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FChalmers added: "None of this matters
OL,7,Fif nobody sees it. Yes, it will change
OL,8,Fthe lives of those who compete but
OL,9,Factually we would want for those
OL,10,Fpeople to be empowered to change the
OL,11,Flives of those who watch it.
OL,13,F"So we want people to come all across
OL,14,Fthe world, certainly throughout this
OL,15,Fcountry, to come to the games in one
OL,16,Fyear's time and we would love them to
OL,17,Fbe travelling on this."
OL,26,@nD@QOUuD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
