PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FThe train, wrapped in black and gold
OL,7,FInvictus branding, will run for at
OL,8,Fleast a year across the London
OL,9,FNorthwestern Railway and West Midlands
OL,10,FRailway networks, on routes that may
OL,11,Ftake visitors to the games.
OL,13,FThe name was picked after a public
OL,14,Fcompetition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FJonny Wiseman, the customer experience
OL,7,Fand commercial director for London
OL,8,FNorthwestern Railway and West Midlands
OL,9,FRailway, said the Invictus Games 2027
OL,10,Fin Birmingham will be a "hugely
OL,11,Fsignificant moment for both the city
OL,12,Fand the country".
OL,26,@rD@YOUtD@PO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FHe hoped the eye-catching train will
OL,7,Finspire customers to learn more about
OL,8,Fthe Invictus Movement, adding: "With
OL,9,Fmore than a million passengers using
OL,10,Four services every week, this
OL,11,Fdistinctive train will fast become a
OL,12,Ffeature of the railway in the lead-up
OL,13,Fto the Birmingham Invictus Games and
OL,14,Fbeyond."
OL,16,FHelen D'Oyley, chief growth officer at
OL,17,Fthe Invictus Games Foundation, hoped
OL,18,Fthe train would help spark curiosity
OL,19,Fwherever it travels.
OL,26,@pD@`OUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FShe said: "Every day, thousands of
OL,7,Fpeople will see this train, travel on
OL,8,Fit, or pass it in stations across the
OL,9,FLondon Northwestern Railway and West
OL,10,FMidlands network.
OL,12,F"Each journey is another opportunity
OL,13,Fto spark curiosity and start
OL,14,Fconversations about the incredible
OL,15,Fresilience of wounded, injured and
OL,16,Fsick service personnel and veterans".
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
