FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783714849
OL,3,CSpecial train unveiled to mark one-
OL,4,Cyear countdown to Invictus Games
OL,6,FInvictus Games Birmingham 2027 chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Helen Helliwell added:
OL,8,F"Birmingham is the destination for
OL,9,Fmany from across the UK and our
OL,10,Fallies, with countless wounded,
OL,11,Finjured and sick service personnel
OL,12,Fbeginning their recovery journey here."
OL,14,FShe said the Spirit of Invictus would
OL,15,Fhelp take people to the NEC
OL,16,FBirmingham, which will "proudly host"
OL,17,Fthe Invictus Games Birmingham 2027.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@gO]xD@XOUxD@eO]
